snippet.title: Rendezvous Delano
snippet.description: Video of a homebrew Nintendo DS game by DeProgrammer. Rendezvous Delano is essentially a mix between Metroid and any generic shoot-em-up game. Various classic Metroid elements are included, such as Samus's ship, exploration, morph ball, energy tanks, and wave beam. The web page and ROM have been uploaded here: http://dpmm.110mb.com/rd/index.html
